  "description": "The cave became a cathedral of resonance. bodyFeedback=0.7, bodyMix=1.0, bodyChar=1. At these settings the Cave comb filter is self-sustaining — each note becomes an organ pipe that speaks back to you in the underwater dark. Gothic architecture assembled from water and limestone.",
