    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "vol": "Transcendental Vol 1",
    "scripture": [
      "The cave became a cathedral by accumulation — one drip, one resonance, ten thousand years.",
      "bodyFeedback=0.7: the cave sustains its own memory of your note.",
      "bodyMix=1.0: the cathedral is everything. The player is incidental."
    ],
    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "WRECK macro adds the steel character to the limestone — the cathedral was once a ship. Slowly increase WRECK to transform gothic stone into industrial ruin. Never exceed bodyFeedback=0.8 or the cave holds the note forever. That is a choice you can make.",
    "diagnosis": "bodyFeedback=0.7: near self-sustaining comb resonance — the cathedral sings back. bodyMix=1.0: total body dominance, the direct signal is architecture. bodyChar=1 (Cave): the specifically detuned comb that makes this haunting rather than clean. filterCutoff=400: mid-depth, the gothic stone has warmth."
  },
